{"tid":218231,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企幅牆好撚多牆蚤(卜泥)","createTime":"2017-04-26T10:54:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T15:43:12.000Z","uid":16404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d380845e931aaa9a5a0506f99effbc12a23cbaf","tid":218231,"uid":16404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:54:28.000Z","msg":"兩年前開始出現<br />\n 試過漂白水抹成間屋 兩星期左右出返哂黎<br />\n<br />\n因為啲卜泥數量好撚多 <br />\n啲傢私 梳化 床全部貼牆 驚抹個陣走到周圍都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以一直都係冬天等佢地唔出現先抹牆大清潔<br />\n點撚知今年冇冬天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幅牆就一直有卜泥 呢排潮濕仲愈黎愈多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咩biokill橙色紫色都試過 <br />\n正面噴蟲之後啲biokill乾左 隻蟲完全冇事 行得走得<br />\n<br />\n最近仲見到天花板都一堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫屋企人重新油牆又話啲油貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔係買唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幅牆油左成十年啦已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n天花板有圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/26/185058_e132808d23370e916936d9eb0bede91b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F26%2F185058_e132808d23370e916936d9eb0bede91b.jpg&h=4630c4c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DW9qB2g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDW9qB2g.jpg&h=8fd8ead6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n煙彈有冇用？求介紹<br />\n<br />\n邊隻牆漆好？"},{"pid":"f098afe0b938982312e95a10e6a40e48454da84d","tid":218231,"uid":90839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:58:41.000Z","msg":"屋企都出現過 留明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c837725256274873ee0a7a57c0593a878aaaa919","tid":218231,"uid":43414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:08:58.000Z","msg":"勤力啲抽濕就唔會有"},{"pid":"3979eea66306a7502ffb7e8314bcd893bb4b4a43","tid":218231,"uid":30918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:10:12.000Z","msg":"澳洲綠水，抽濕"},{"pid":"9a6993a8f4ee9bcb5d26cd52013f5065cec94e70","tid":218231,"uid":90117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:11:32.000Z","msg":"試過有 最後用左漂白水抹。用過兩個滅蚤蛋。最後洗過所有衫。大清潔完就未見過佢。"},{"pid":"cfb42341b1cafa64bc7e6ec77dcde45b0ee32848","tid":218231,"uid":26115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:12:43.000Z","msg":"上年都好多，今年油過油就冇事"},{"pid":"1663546699947138e39eb421f4fc0017c708ce74","tid":218231,"uid":16404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T12:11:50.000Z","msg":"原來咁多人有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26545f2846f255d9ee0dd9347a6fb63bc00a86c4","tid":218231,"uid":16404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:13:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f0edf00dc9c9a69b31ad317c3072b1a079c38c","tid":218231,"uid":90054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:20:27.000Z","msg":"原來好多人都有<br />\n我屋企試過黎過隻壁虎<br />\n我睇住佢係我牆上一啖一隻<br />\n不停開餐 跟住就冇哂<br />\n但好似佢走左之後 蟲仔又出番黎"},{"pid":"0e73df94be9c2e82feae5f5b8e53bb139d740993","tid":218231,"uid":50610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:21:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來好多人都有<br />\n我屋企試過黎過隻壁虎<br />\n我睇住佢係我牆上一啖一隻<br />\n不停開餐 跟住就冇哂<br />\n但好似佢走左之後 蟲仔又出番黎</blockquote><br />\n留住神獸真係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65109ad8519312c6fdb1d3a2ba792c45e62666d0","tid":218231,"uid":1625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T14:22:29.000Z","msg":"油有幾貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/no